ygData.subject: Need info for Rathyl room
ygData.msgSnippet: I got the skull key from Bonecracker, silver key from Derz and golden key from najena, but none of them open the door to Rathly room (the underground cell,
ygData.messageBody:
I got the skull key from Bonecracker, silver key from Derz and golden key
from najena, but none of them open the door to Rathly room (the underground
cell, need to go thru the 3 magi cells 1st). Anyone know who drop Rathyl's
key? Simi lvl? Rathyl drop hollowed bone bracers (sell 200-300pp) and
25/50% (?) wt-lost bag/pouch. The room is always empty too. Rathyl is a
SK which can revive after he got killed, ie need to kill him 2 times.

Just another hunting spots for the lvl 30s ;)
